{"tid":927062,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 如果冇辦法係外面達到高潮，係咪應該再繼續落去？","createTime":"2018-12-04T02:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T06:33:41.000Z","uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61fa02305872f3fcf24c93289de3f044c271c7fb","tid":927062,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n一路以黎，都好密下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差唔多日日都有（唔信就算）<br />\n但真係未試過一次係外面去到高潮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用分數計的話<br />\n1－10分，通常都只係得 1－2分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有諗過其實係咪我有問題<br />\n但自覺係一般正正常常咁 <br />\n所以我係到諗係出面高潮係咪必須？<br />\n<br />\n講返入面，好多時都可以有高潮<br />\n雖然其實咁係好正常<br />\n話晒投資左唔少，梗係落力好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係就顯得出面要俾更多錢，都去唔到高潮真係好蠢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再諗諗<br />\n根本唔係出面洗幾多錢嘅問題<br />\n而係對方質素唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次都係對方太慢，快唔到又點高潮呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終呢d 都係雙方面計<br />\n聽人講係外面，要去到盡的話<br />\n多 peer 先有機會有高潮 ... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以計我話！<br />\n裝 1000M 寬頻真係好傻仔<br />\n200M 光纖就夠晒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween，有冇人試過 寬頻高潮 爆晒1000M 咁 up／download？"},{"pid":"495b6473261da001c32ce26b2c37fb0ed11eff50","tid":927062,"uid":5995,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"唔知up乜鳩"},{"pid":"683b21c4ba4d92d566a0ddcae7a039d033c24e73","tid":927062,"uid":45772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"你係唔係覺得自己好幽默？"},{"pid":"0e4c60b3f5fa1f847754c854284b4c3fe219ee04","tid":927062,"uid":78971,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"it蠢撚懶風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經想像到啲女聽完你講嘢之後個樣"},{"pid":"1f44d7565da17f8563dfaaf6cd4718c2d23b7b44","tid":927062,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>it毒撚懶風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經想像到啲女聽完你講嘢之後個樣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ed476ed4f22fbd5426048bdd36bde9816de5c0a6","tid":927062,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e4c60b3f5fa1f847754c854284b4c3fe219ee04","tid":927062,"uid":78971,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"it蠢撚懶風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經想像到啲女聽完你講嘢之後個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"it 狗係咁悶毒嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇野做就等炒<br />\n有野做就仆街"},{"pid":"9b5015a92f32e5c57fca359f7f1a0a1ed31fd572","tid":927062,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"怪不得永遠a0"},{"pid":"46e522777c279313b5ad5fa905a62b059b6068b0","tid":927062,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"topic已經唔撚知你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02e1e3fdfdc8e7e70a9aa54b17b5b7b0cb89aef","tid":927062,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46e522777c279313b5ad5fa905a62b059b6068b0","tid":927062,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"topic已經唔撚知你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"原來打漏左個唔字 ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果冇辦法係外面達到高潮，係咪<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>應該再繼續落去？"},{"pid":"33f88b9d2f485ac4a564ba88244ab94